headline: Gilead Joins Partners for Delivery of First Shipments of Breakthrough Twice-yearly Lenacapavir for HIV Prevention to Sub-Saharan Africa
summary: FOSTER CITY, Calif. & MBABANE, Eswatini, November 18, 2025--Gilead Sciences, Inc. (Nasdaq: GILD) today announced the delivery of first shipments of lenacapavir – Gilead’s twice-yearly injectable HIV-1 capsid inhibitor – for the prevention of HIV as pre-exposure prophylaxis (PrEP) to Eswatini and Zambia.
